reviews.text:
So, was a little scared at mixing this one up, but all the parts came in the Awesome box, so I figured what the hell.  Gotta tell ya, it's not one that I would have thought of in a LONG time.  The cream blend is there, but I don't think I would put it in the Milkshake category, but that is very subjective.  It's a nice smooth vape with just a hint of mint, which I guess it to be expected.  Oh yeah, and the ever slight touch of Banana. &#xD;
&#xD;
Nice combo - keep them coming...
